'''瓦隆主要矿业遗址'''（{{lang-en|'''Major Mining Sites of Wallonia'''}}）位于比利时南部的瓦隆区<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.travelpulse.com/unesco-adds-wallonia-mining-sites-in-belgium-to-world-heritage-list.html |title=UNESCO Adds Wallonia Mining Sites in Belgium to World Heritage List |publisher=Travel Pulse |date=2012-07-17 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723001723/http://www.travelpulse.com/unesco-adds-wallonia-mining-sites-in-belgium-to-world-heritage-list.html |archive-date=2012-07-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。它完整保留了18到20世纪的瓦隆地区煤矿的原貌，并具有多处和煤矿基础设施的遗迹，2012年被列入世界文化遗产<ref>{{cite web|title=世界遗产官网|url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/1344|accessdate=2013-12-24|archive-date=2012-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703213428/http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/1344|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

